### Test NongTimeAI Timesheet API

### 0. Health Check - Service Status
GET https://localhost:7000/api/health

### 0.1 Health Check - Ollama Connectivity
GET https://localhost:7000/api/health/ollama

### 1. Process Complete Timesheet Message
POST https://localhost:7000/api/timesheet/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "แก้บั๊กหน้าล็อกอิน 2 ชม."
}

### 2. Process Incomplete Message (No Hours)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/timesheet/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "ประชุมทีม"
}

### 3. Process Task Message
POST https://localhost:7000/api/timesheet/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "ทำ API สำหรับ User Management 3.5 ชม."
}

